{"format":"tiptap/v1","updatedAt":"2026-06-21T00:32:03.953Z","doc":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Prompt versioning"},{"type":"text","text":" is the practice of treating prompts as "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"managed, trackable assets"},{"type":"text","text":"—similar to source code—enabling teams to track changes, reproduce past behavior, and roll back safely without redeploying application code."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"The key insight:"},{"type":"text","text":" \"Prompts often act as the source code for your AI's behavior.\""}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Why Version Prompts?"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"1. Track Changes Systematically"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Versioning allows you to systematically track changes and compare the performance of different prompt variations through A/B testing.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Benefits:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Clear history"},{"type":"text","text":" — See what changed, when, and why\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Compare variations"},{"type":"text","text":" — A/B test different prompts\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Ownership"},{"type":"text","text":" — Track who made changes"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"2. Ensure Reproducibility"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"By locking your application to a specific prompt version, you can ensure consistent behavior and reliable outputs.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Why reproducibility matters:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Debug production"},{"type":"text","text":" — Trace outputs back to exact prompt\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Reproduce issues"},{"type":"text","text":" — Replicate past behavior\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Audit compliance"},{"type":"text","text":" — Meet regulatory requirements"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"3. Enable Safe Rollback"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"If a new version causes problems, you can easily roll back to a previously known good version.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Rollback methods:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Feature flag rollback"},{"type":"text","text":" — Instantly switch to previous version\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Git revert"},{"type":"text","text":" — Merge revert PR to restore old version\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Database migration"},{"type":"text","text":" — Keep "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"previous_version"},{"type":"text","text":" column for one-click restoration"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"4. Decouple from Application Releases"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Prompt versioning infrastructure allows prompt changes to ship independently of application code releases. Teams can hotfix a prompt or roll back to a previous version without redeploying the application binary, which shortens iteration cycles and limits the impact of any single change.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Benefits:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Hotfix prompts"},{"type":"text","text":" — Fix issues without redeploying app\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Shorter cycles"},{"type":"text","text":" — Faster iteration\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Limited impact"},{"type":"text","text":" — Smaller blast radius"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Best Practices for Prompt Versioning"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"1. Assign Version ID to Every Change"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Assign a version ID to every prompt change\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Production consequence:"},{"type":"text","text":" Clear version identifiers make it possible to trace any production output back to the exact prompt that generated it"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Approaches:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Semantic versioning"},{"type":"text","text":" — "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"MAJOR.MINOR.PATCH"},{"type":"text","text":" (e.g., "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"1.2.3"},{"type":"text","text":")\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Content-addressable IDs"},{"type":"text","text":" — Unique ID from content hash (e.g., "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"5878bd218351fb8e"},{"type":"text","text":")\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Smart labels"},{"type":"text","text":" — "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"{feature}-{purpose}-{version}"},{"type":"text","text":" (e.g., "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"support-chat-tone-v2"},{"type":"text","text":")"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"2. Adopt Semantic Versioning (SemVer)"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Semantic versioning (SemVer) is a proven framework for tracking changes in software and is equally effective for prompt management. Use a three-part version number (X.Y.Z):\""}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Version Part"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"When to Increment"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Example"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Meaning"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Major (X)"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Significant structural changes"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"2.0.0"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Overhauling prompt framework"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Minor (Y)"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"New features or context parameters"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"1.3.0"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Adding new evaluation criteria"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Patch (Z)"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Small fixes"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"1.2.3"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Correcting typos or minor tweaks"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Example version history:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"text"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"v1.0.0 — Initial prompt\nv1.0.1 — Fixed typo in instructions\nv1.1.0 — Added few-shot examples\nv1.2.0 — Added output format schema\nv2.0.0 — Complete framework overhaul"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"3. Version Prompts Together with Models & Parameters"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Version prompts together with models and parameters\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Production consequence:"},{"type":"text","text":" Prompt behavior depends on the full execution context, so tracking prompt text alone is not enough to reproduce or debug production behavior"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Track together:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Prompt text"},{"type":"text","text":" — The actual instructions\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Model version"},{"type":"text","text":" — e.g., "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"claude-3.5-sonnet"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Parameters"},{"type":"text","text":" — Temperature, max tokens, top_p\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Variables"},{"type":"text","text":" — Runtime substitution values"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Example:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"json"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"prompt_version\": \"1.2.3\",\n  \"model\": \"claude-3.5-sonnet\",\n  \"temperature\": 0.7,\n  \"max_tokens\": 1000,\n  \"variables\": {\n    \"topic\": \"AI automation\",\n    \"audience\": \"technical managers\"\n  }\n}"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"4. Keep Prompt Versions Immutable After Deployment"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Keep prompt versions immutable after deployment\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Production consequence:"},{"type":"text","text":" Immutability ensures that logs, traces, and evaluations always refer to the same prompt version and makes rollback reliable"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"How to enforce:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Never edit deployed versions"},{"type":"text","text":" — Create new version for changes\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Content-addressable IDs"},{"type":"text","text":" — Same content always produces same ID\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Locked in registry"},{"type":"text","text":" — Prevent accidental modification"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"5. Track Templates and Variables Alongside Text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Track templates and variables alongside prompt text\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Production consequence:"},{"type":"text","text":" Changes to template structure or variable handling can affect outputs as much as text changes and should be visible and reviewable"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Track:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Template structure"},{"type":"text","text":" — The prompt framework\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Variable schema"},{"type":"text","text":" — Expected input types\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Few-shot examples"},{"type":"text","text":" — Training data in prompt\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Metadata"},{"type":"text","text":" — Tags, descriptions, owners"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"6. Use Environment-Based Deployment"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Effective prompt version control separates versions across distinct environments.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Three environments:"}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Environment"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Purpose"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Version Behavior"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Development"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Rapid iteration, experimentation"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Latest version, always changing"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Staging"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Final validation, mirrors production"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Specific tested version"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Production"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Live traffic, stable"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Pinned version, immutable"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Environment workflow:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n1. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Develop"},{"type":"text","text":" — Experiment freely, refine behavior\n2. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Staging"},{"type":"text","text":" — Test in production-like conditions\n3. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Promote"},{"type":"text","text":" — Production points to new version\n4. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Previous version"},{"type":"text","text":" — Remains available for rollback"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"How to implement:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"python"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Load prompt with environment parameter\nprompt = loadPrompt(\n    name=\"assistant-prompt\",\n    environment=\"production\"  # Picks pinned version\n)"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"7. Run Automated Evaluations on Every Change"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Run automated evaluations on every prompt change\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Production consequence:"},{"type":"text","text":" Automated checks catch regressions early and prevent unvalidated prompt updates from reaching production"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Evaluation pipeline:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n1. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Create test cases"},{"type":"text","text":" — Curated datasets\n2. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Run test suite"},{"type":"text","text":" — Execute against dataset\n3. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"LLM-judge scoring"},{"type":"text","text":" — Automated evaluation\n4. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Validation rubrics"},{"type":"text","text":" — Quality criteria\n5. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Pass/fail"},{"type":"text","text":" — Block deployment if fails"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"8. Use Human Review for High-Risk Cases"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Use human review for high-risk or ambiguous cases\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"When human review needed:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Sensitive domains"},{"type":"text","text":" — Healthcare, legal, finance\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Ambiguous outputs"},{"type":"text","text":" — Automated metrics can't provide judgment\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Complex decisions"},{"type":"text","text":" — Require human context"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"9. Store Prompts in Version Control (Git)"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Store your prompts in version control alongside your code whenever possible. This approach brings all the benefits of modern development workflows to prompt management systems.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Benefits:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Detailed change history"},{"type":"text","text":" — See all modifications\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Branch-based development"},{"type":"text","text":" — Experimental prompts without affecting production\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Easy rollbacks"},{"type":"text","text":" — Git revert to restore old version\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Clear ownership"},{"type":"text","text":" — Pull request reviews\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"CI/CD integration"},{"type":"text","text":" — Automated tests on changes"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Git-based structure:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"text"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"prompts/\n  ├── customer-support-triage.md\n  ├── code-review-assistant.md\n  ├── blog-post-writer.md\n  └── changelog.md"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Principles:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Dedicated prompt directory"},{"type":"text","text":" — Separate from app code\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"One file per prompt"},{"type":"text","text":" — Granular change tracking\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Semantic naming"},{"type":"text","text":" — "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"customer-support-triage.md"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"10. Document Every Change (Change Logs)"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Document Every Change and Monitor Performance\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Change log template:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"markdown"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"## v1.2.3 (2025-01-15)\n**What changed:**\n- Added output format schema for JSON\n- Fixed typo in instruction section\n- Added 2 new few-shot examples\n\n**Why changed:**\n- Required JSON output for API integration\n- Reader reported confusing instruction\n- Limited examples causing poor quality\n\n**Who changed:**\n- Author: john@company.com\n- Reviewer: jane@company.com\n\n**Performance metrics:**\n- Success rate: 85% → 92% (+7%)\n- Error rate: 15% → 8% (-7%)\n- User satisfaction: 3.8 → 4.5 (+0.7)"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Prompt Versioning Tools"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"1. Braintrust"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Automatic versioning with content-addressable IDs: Every prompt change receives a unique version ID derived from content. The same prompt always produces the same ID, ensuring reproducibility.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Features:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Content-addressable IDs"},{"type":"text","text":" — e.g., "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"5878bd218351fb8e"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Immutability"},{"type":"text","text":" — Versions never change\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Environment-based deployment"},{"type":"text","text":" — dev/staging/prod\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"A/B testing"},{"type":"text","text":" — Compare versions"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"2. MLflow Prompt Registry"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"MLflow has this prompt management tool. You can do this in two different ways: through UI or with the code.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"UI capabilities:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- Create prompt\n- Create prompt version\n- Compare variants\n- Delete versions"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Code automation:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"python"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"import mlflow.genai as genai\n\ngenai.register_prompt(\n    name=\"invoice_extraction\",\n    template=\"Extract invoice data from: {{invoice_text}}\"\n)"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"3. Promptplex"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Keep track of changes, roll back to previous versions, and maintain a clean history.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Features:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Centralized templates"},{"type":"text","text":" — All prompts in one place\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Versioned"},{"type":"text","text":" — Track changes, rollback\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Render anywhere"},{"type":"text","text":" — Use in content tool, chatbot"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"4. Agente"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Learn how to version LLM prompts for teams. Covers Git-based approaches, dedicated systems, three integration paths, and step-by-step setup.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Features:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Git-based"},{"type":"text","text":" — Version control integration\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Dedicated systems"},{"type":"text","text":" — Prompt management platforms\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Integration paths"},{"type":"text","text":" — Multiple approaches"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Real-World Versioning Workflow"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Step-by-Step Process"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"1. Audit Current Prompts"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"text"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"List every prompt in production\nNote where each one lives (code, config, database, spreadsheet)\nIdentify owner for each prompt"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"2. Move to Versioning System"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"sql"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Import prompts into dedicated platform\nCreate one project per application/use case\nApply semantic versioning (X.Y.Z)"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"3. Set Up Environment Separation"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"text"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Development → Rapid iteration, latest version\nStaging → Mirrors production, tested version\nProduction → Pinned version, immutable"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"4. Implement Evaluation Pipeline"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"text"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Automated tests on every change\nLLM-judge scoring\nValidation rubrics\nPass/fail blocking"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"5. Enable Rollback Capability"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"text"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Feature flag rollback (instant)\nGit revert (merge revert PR)\nDatabase migration (previous_version column)"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Summary"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Prompt versioning"},{"type":"text","text":" treats prompts as managed, trackable assets:"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Why version:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n1. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Track changes"},{"type":"text","text":" — Systematic history\n2. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Ensure reproducibility"},{"type":"text","text":" — Lock to specific version\n3. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Enable rollback"},{"type":"text","text":" — Roll back to known good version\n4. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Decouple from app"},{"type":"text","text":" — Hotfix without redeploying"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Best practices:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n1. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Assign version ID"},{"type":"text","text":" — Every change tracked\n2. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Semantic versioning"},{"type":"text","text":" — "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"MAJOR.MINOR.PATCH"},{"type":"text","text":"\n3. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"typ